00:36:55.450 --> 00:36:58.620
that I wrote about in the book were
my neighbors in the trailer park.

00:36:58.620 --> 00:37:01.760
And the landlords were really keen

00:37:01.760 --> 00:37:03.920
on just people understanding
their work.

00:37:03.920 --> 00:37:05.740
You know, they were
proud of their work.

00:37:05.740 --> 00:37:07.680
They often were, like,
self-starters, you know,

00:37:07.680 --> 00:37:10.770
and built a kind of
business up from nothing

00:37:10.770 --> 00:37:13.110
and they were interested in that.

00:37:13.110 --> 00:37:16.440
That doesn't mean it was easy all
